OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778691956
OL,3,CFire at Garvagh car showroom believed
OL,4,Cto be deliberate
OL,6,FA major fire at a car showroom in a Co
OL,7,FLondonderry village is thought to have
OL,8,Fbeen deliberate.
OL,10,FAround 55 firefighters were battling
OL,11,Fthe blaze at the scene at Carhill
OL,12,FRoad, Garvagh, in the early hours of
OL,13,FWednesday.
OL,15,FThe Northern Ireland Fire & Rescue
OL,16,FService (NIFRS) said they believe it
OL,17,Fwas deliberate, and police are
OL,18,Finvestigating the incident as arson.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
