OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778691956
OL,3,CFire at Garvagh car showroom believed
OL,4,Cto be deliberate
OL,6,FAn NIFRS spokesperson said they were
OL,7,Fcalled to a report of a building fire
OL,8,Fat 4.30am.
OL,10,F"On arrival crews were met with a
OL,11,Fdeveloped fire involving a car
OL,12,Fshowroom, vehicles and cafe premises,"
OL,13,Fthey said.
OL,15,F"Crews utilised firefighting jets and
OL,16,Fan aerial ladder jet to resolve the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@fO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778691956
OL,3,CFire at Garvagh car showroom believed
OL,4,Cto be deliberate
OL,6,F"At the height of the incident 55
OL,7,Ffirefighters were involved. A total of
OL,8,Fsix appliances attended from Maghera,
OL,9,FKilrea, Dungiven, Ballymoney and
OL,10,FColeraine stations, supported by an
OL,11,Faerial ladder appliance from Northland
OL,12,Fstation, a command support unit from
OL,13,FStrabane station and a water tanker
OL,14,Ffrom Dungiven station.
OL,16,F"The incident was resolved by 7.47am
OL,17,Fand the cause is believed to be
OL,18,Fdeliberate."
OL,20,FA police spokesperson made an appeal
OL,21,Fto the public for information.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
