OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1778691956
OL,3,CFire at Garvagh car showroom believed
OL,4,Cto be deliberate
OL,6,F"At approximately 5am, we received a
OL,7,Freport of a fire at a business in the
OL,8,FCarhill Road area," they said.
OL,10,F"Officers attended, along with
OL,11,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,12,FFire and Rescue Service, who
OL,13,Fextinguished the blaze.
OL,15,F"This is being treated as arson and
OL,16,Fenquiries are ongoing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]rD@AOUwD@AOU
