OL,3,CFire at Garvagh car showroom believed
OL,4,Cto be deliberate
OL,6,F"I am appealing to anyone who may have
OL,7,Fwitnessed anyone suspicious in the
OL,8,Farea or to anyone with CCTV, doorbell
OL,9,For other footage that could assist the
OL,10,Finvestigation, to contact police on
OL,11,F101, quoting reference number 146 13/
OL,12,F05/26."
